    "name": "Published hemolysis correlation literature review",
    "description": "A systematic review of published hemolysis power-law correlations (Giersiepen, Zhang, Heuser-Opitz) and prior CFD hemolysis studies for centrifugal blood pumps was conducted. Predicted hemolysis index values from the present CFD model were compared against ranges reported in the reviewed literature. The review covered 34 peer-reviewed publications spanning 1990–2024 and concluded that CFD predictions fall within the envelope of published experimental ranges, supporting model credibility.",
    "activityType": "literature-review"
  },
